data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home built in 1994. With a spacious 1,404 sq. ft.  of living space, this residence offers comfort and style. The third bedroom is currently used as an office space, perfect for those who work from home or need a dedicated workspace. The property features two inviting living spaces, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well-maintained and thoughtfully designed house your new home.
